data.description: Welcome to The Woodlands at Fishers Creek! Nestled on over a third of a acre,this dream home offers a floor plan that flows open from foyer  through living room,dining room & into the spacious family room!The gourmet kitchen is a must see! Equipped with stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, a double sink, granite counter tops, plenty of cabinetry, walk in pantry, chef’s island & an adjoining morning room!The oak stairs & metal railings guide the way upward towards the four bedrooms with the primary bedroom being the masterpiece! Featuring a tray ceiling, seating area, double walk in closets & a Roman shower! Also on the second floor is a spacious loft, great for multiple uses! Outside there’s a large porch, a two car garage & plenty of driveway space.The back yard is great for family fun, equipped with wood decking & pergola. Also included is a Barefoot Spania 19 Swim spa!Great for exercise, therapy, family fun and good ol relaxation!This house is a must see, schedule a tour today!
